Introduction

Park Chaerin, mononymously known as Chaerin is a South Korean dancer, rapper and singer under FNC Entertainment, FNC W and KM Entertainment. She was a member and the Main Dancer, Vocalist and Rapper of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet.

On January 21, 2019, she made her official debut as a member of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet with the single mini album "Let's Play Cherry Bullet" with "Q & A" serving as the title track.

In 2023, Chaerin was a constant of the survival of the Mnet's survival show "Queendom Puzzle". She was eliminated as she was ranked 26th.
